name: PagesJaunes
overview: PagesJaunes Groupe operates as a publisher of printed and online directories in France and internationally. The company publishes printed directories under the PagesJaunes directory and L’Annuaire names; and online directories under pagesjaunes.fr and PagesJaunes 3611 names. It also involves in the provision of online services; telephone directory enquiry services; Web site creation and hosting service for businesses; publication of the PagesPro directories and the QuiDonc reverse directory; publication of consumer directories and Kompass directories; direct marketing services; and geographic services of maps. In addition, the company engages in the sale of online access to databases; and advertising space in printed and online directories. PagesJaunes Groupe is based in Sevres, France.
